he wrists to the rest of your arms, whereas straps add extra support to help you lift heavier poundage. If maximizing your deadlifts is your ultimate goal, invest in a quality pair of lifting straps. Another downside to lifting hooks is that they do not offer the opportunity to fail a rep, as the barbell is hooked to the weightlifting hook. This means that come what may, you will have to perform the eccentric movement, even in case of failure.</p></div></div><div data-label="Liquid" data-key="liquid" data-atomgroup="module" id="m-1673379838180" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-liquid" data-ver="1.1" data-id="1673379838180" data-name="Right click on this, and choose Edit Code."><div class="module gf_module- gf_module--lg gf_module--md gf_module--sm gf_module--xs {{extraClass}}"><!-- Begin Mailchimp Signup Form --><style>.evg-mail-form h3 {margin-top: 0;}.evg-mail-form {margin: 50px 0;border-radius: 7px;border: 1px solid #bbbbbb;padding: 22px;padding-right: 50px;position: relative;font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;}.evg-mail-form__grid {display: grid;grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;align-items: center;gap: 50px;}.evg-mail-form__image {max-width: 100%;border-radius: 7px;}.evg-mail-form__inputs {display: grid;grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap: 15px 10px;}.evg-mail-form__inputs #mce-responses {grid-column: 1/4;}.evg-mail-form__inputs input {width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 17px;padding: 10px 10px;border: 1px solid #bbb;outline: none;box-shadow: none;background-color: white;font-weight: 400;font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;}.evg-mail-form__inputs input.mce_inline_error {border-color: red !important;}.evg-mail-form__inputs input[type="submit"] {text-transform: uppercase;background-color: #ef0404;color: white;border: none;outline: none;box-shadow: none;cursor: pointer;font-weight: 700;border-radius: 5px;font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;}.evg-mail-form__checkbox {display: grid;grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;gap: 10px;font-size: 14px;grid-column: